----------------------------------------------------------------
PROCEDURE TO FINAL GALLEYS
----------------------------------------------------------------

0) If necessary, convert the DOCX/ODT/ODF file to tex using ???
exemple:
> ?????

1) Enter final metadata in tex
exemple tex file:  "seismica_template.tex" 

2) Use the galley seismica.cls to produce the galley PDF

3) Use tex2xml.sh to convert the tex file to JATS XML that can be read by OJS
exemple:
> ./tex2xml.sh seismica_template biblio

4) If TABLES, tex2xml.sh will export two files for each table: tabxx.tex and tabxx.xml
for each table:
- replace the wrong table code in the galley XML by tabxx.xml
- translate the tabxx.tex to HTML with https://tableconvert.com/latex-to-html
- copy the HTML code in the XML galley

5) Upload the galley PDF and XML files to the OJS website. 
For XML, images need to be uploaded separately (no need to fill in the caption etc.)
